      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about like, getting drunk or anything. just the one glass of wine i always have. i've read that alcohol can actually make sedatives work more effectively to knock you out. is there really that much of a difference between a normal dinner glass and something that would actually be \"dangerous\"?",
